Package org.sbml.jsbml.validator

This package provides methods to validate the content of SBML models, whether given in a file or as a data structure.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
OverdeterminationValidator This class creates a bipartite graph and a matching for the given model using the algorithm by Hopcroft and Karp (1973).
SBMLValidator Validates the SBML document given by filename.xml or located at the http:// URL.
 

Enum Summary
SBMLValidator.CHECK_CATEGORY Enumerates the different possible check categories when performing the validation of an SBML document.
 

Exception Summary
ModelOverdeterminedException This class represents an exception that is thrown when the model to be simulated is overdetermined
 

Package org.sbml.jsbml.validator Description

This package provides methods to validate the content of SBML models, whether given in a file or as a data structure.
